Accessing Small SemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid AllSmallSemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic semicommutativeternarygroupoid models from orders 2 to 3.
The models are generated by Mace4 , using the definitions in Section .
